  "novel_contributions": [
    "We present the Vision Mixture of Experts (V-MoE), a distributed sparsely-activated Transformer model for vision.",
    "We propose Batch Prioritized Routing, a priority-based routing algorithm that allows V-MoEs to discard the least useful tokens.",
    "We show that V-MoE models can be stably trained, seamlessly used for transfer, and successfully fine-tuned with as few as 1 000 datapoints.",
    "We train a 15B parameter model that attains 90.35% on ImageNet.",
    "We demonstrate that V-MoE can match the performance of state-of-the-art dense models while requiring as little as half of the compute at inference time."
  ],
